data.description: Step into a newly revitalized & impeccably designed 3-bedroom, 2-bath luxury villa, featuring a spacious open floor plan w/ a gourmet kitchen adorned w/ exquisite granite countertops & designer elements. Cathedral ceilings soar above, creating a seamless connection to the generously sized living room, perfect setting for entertaining. Each bedroom offers private entrances providing versatile options for in-laws.. leading to a charming screen-in courtyard over 880 sf . Features ALL UPDATED WIND & DOORS, NEW ROOF 2020, NEW PLUMBING, 2022 AC system & tank-less water heater.  Boca Gardens HOA FEE INCLUDES INSURANCE, ROOF, LANDSCAPING.  - 2 assigned parking spaces & NO association approval required. PETS welcome.  A-Rated Schools . FHA BUYERS WELCOME
